## 1. Property-Based Tests (PBT)

### PBT-01: tool\_use\_id Passthrough Invariant

| Field | Value |
| --- | --- |
| **ID** | PBT-01 |
| **Priority** | Critical |
| **Type** | Property-Based Test |
| **Requirement** | BR-1, BR-2, UC-1 Step 6-7 |
| **Tools** | proptest (Rust) |
| **File** | kiro-rs/src/anthropic/tests/id\_passthrough\_test.rs |
| **Preconditions** | proptest crate configured |

**Property:** For ALL strings id matching pattern tooluse\_[A-Za-z0-9]{8,32}: - convert\_tool\_use\_block(ApiBlock { id, .. }).id == id - No ID generation function is called during conversion

**Test Steps:**

| Step | Action | Expected Result |
| --- | --- | --- |
| 1 | Generate 1000+ random tool\_use\_id strings matching tooluse\_[A-Za-z0-9]+ | Valid IDs generated |
| 2 | For each ID, create mock ApiToolUseBlock and pass to convert\_tool\_use\_block() | Function returns Ok(SseContentBlock) |
| 3 | Assert output SseContentBlock.id == input ID | All assertions pass — no transformation |

**Test Data:** Random strings generated by proptest: tooluse\_[A-Za-z0-9]{8,32}

### PBT-02: History Storage Preserves Arbitrary IDs

| Field | Value |
| --- | --- |
| **ID** | PBT-02 |
| **Priority** | Critical |
| **Type** | Property-Based Test |
| **Requirement** | BR-2, UC-1 Step 7 |
| **Tools** | proptest (Rust) |
| **File** | kiro-rs/src/anthropic/tests/id\_passthrough\_test.rs |
| **Preconditions** | ConversationHistory struct available |

**Property:** For ALL valid tool\_use\_id strings stored via push\_assistant\_message(): - history.find\_tool\_use(id) returns Some(\_) - Retrieved block’s id matches stored id exactly

**Test Steps:**

| Step | Action | Expected Result |
| --- | --- | --- |
| 1 | Generate random tool\_use\_id | Valid ID |
| 2 | Store ContentBlock::ToolUse with that ID in history | Storage succeeds |
| 3 | Call find\_tool\_use(id) | Returns Some with matching ID |
| 4 | Assert retrieved\_id == stored\_id (byte-for-byte) | Exact match |

### PBT-03: No ID Collision Across Multiple Blocks

| Field | Value |
| --- | --- |
| **ID** | PBT-03 |
| **Priority** | High |
| **Type** | Property-Based Test |
| **Requirement** | BR-4, BR-5 |
| **Tools** | proptest (Rust) |
| **File** | kiro-rs/src/anthropic/tests/id\_passthrough\_test.rs |
| **Preconditions** | Multiple tool\_use blocks in single response |

**Property:** For ANY list of N distinct tool\_use\_ids stored in history: - All N IDs are independently retrievable - get\_all\_tool\_use\_ids().len() == N - No ID overwrites another

**Test Steps:**

| Step | Action | Expected Result |
| --- | --- | --- |
| 1 | Generate Vec of 2-10 unique random tool\_use\_ids | All unique |
| 2 | Store all as ContentBlock::ToolUse in one assistant message | Storage succeeds |
| 3 | For each ID, call find\_tool\_use(id) | Each returns Some |
| 4 | Assert get\_all\_tool\_use\_ids() contains all generated IDs | All present |

