| **Preconditions** | converter.rs compiled |

**Test Steps:**

| Step | Action | Expected Result |
| --- | --- | --- |
| 1 | Create ApiToolUseBlock { id: "tooluse\_ABC123", name: "readFile", input: {...} } | Block created |
| 2 | Call convert\_tool\_use\_block(&block) | Returns Ok(SseContentBlock::ToolUse { ... }) |
| 3 | Assert result.id == "tooluse\_ABC123" | Exact match — no transformation |

**Test Data:** id = "tooluse\_ABC123", name = "readFile", input = {"path": "/src/main.rs"}

