| **Preconditions** | Mock API returns text-only response |

**Test Steps:**

| Step | Action | Expected Result |
| --- | --- | --- |
| 1 | Configure mock: {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Hello world"}]} | Text response |
| 2 | POST /chat/completions with simple message (no tools) | SSE stream |
| 3 | Parse SSE events | Text content received |
| 4 | Verify message\_stop event at end | Stream completes |
| 5 | Verify no tool\_use events in stream | No false tool detection |
| 6 | Verify no errors, no 400/500 | Clean response |

